scene.message:
Maki: Those people are in the{nl}
same situation as you all,{nl}
aren't they.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: To think a haunted{nl}
house would really have a{nl}
ghost!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Wonderful! To think we{nl}
might even see a ghost...{nl}
Let's hurry and go look!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: If it's the ghost of{nl}
a peerless beauty, maybe it's{nl}
okay...{wait_fr:32} no no, on second{nl}
thought, I'll pass!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase should've brought{nl}
a camera!{waitkey}I'd snap a ton of ghost{nl}
photos and sell them all over!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Scientists cowering{nl}
from ghosts...{wait_fr:32} Kandori sure{nl}
was blessed with fine talent.{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: The truth is, we{nl}
aren't of this world. There's{nl}
a room with a machine to send{nl}
us home, but{waitkey}we can't get in, and it's{nl}
a real problem...{waitkey}{clearbox}Would you please go and{nl}
have a look for us?{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Damn it!{waitkey}{clearbox}That Kandori — after using our{nl}
research to the hilt, to{nl}
leave us behind like this!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: From inside that{nl}
room, you can hear a woman's{nl}
ghost weeping!{waitkey}{clearbox}We say out loud that ghosts{nl}
can't possibly exist, but{waitkey}{clearbox}we're too scared, and no one{nl}
can go near it...{waitkey}{ret}
